{"tid":2454694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(每日一毒)警東九龍搗3麻雀檔及派對房間檢獲毒品　拘捕13人另票控14人","createTime":"2021-03-20T12:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T12:10:12.000Z","uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c1f06379d46d03d64ad60d9311fee37dd89158","tid":2454694,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"東九龍總區刑事部、東九龍總區機動部隊、黃大仙警區、將軍澳警區、觀塘警區及秀茂坪警區，昨日（19日）展開代號「勇爵（BRAVEDUKE）」反罪惡行動，搗破1個非法麻雀賭檔及2間派對房間，檢獲約值11萬元懷疑毒品、約7,000元現金、2部釣魚機、1張麻雀枱和賭博工具等。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，12男1女（20至53歲）涉嫌「經營賭博場所」、「在賭博場所內賭博」、「無牌售賣酒類飲品」、「藏毒」、「販毒」、「藏有工具可作吸食毒品用途」及違反《預防及控制疾病（規定及指示）（業務及處所）規例》（第599F章）被捕，其中4名男子獲准保釋候查，4月中旬向警方報到；其餘人等正被扣查；另亦有12男2女（20至57歲），涉嫌違反《預防及控制疾病（禁止群組聚集）條例》（第599G章）被票控。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：鄧海興<br />\n2021-03-20 05:35<br />\n最後更新日期：2021-03-20 05:35<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a40d3c10a89613b025cc7f7a938e5c7d007088","tid":2454694,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"HI野打牌?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd8680c0cfacc2ad7c767f8d55ac6889f24d5cc","tid":2454694,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a40d3c10a89613b025cc7f7a938e5c7d007088","tid":2454694,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"HI野打牌?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:06:48.000Z","msg":"HI野個人無思想能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d09d73004832d581f9d83b4ca1d0b688acc8714","tid":2454694,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"在賭博場所內賭博<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65328432f723c7814eca173e8758d0abf67a287","tid":2454694,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"12男1女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3bc3302131e1d5990d8dd07736ad1d70af5323","tid":2454694,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"睇人坐監最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}